divs: Sighting Detailswell i have no idea what just happend, I just went outside to have a smoke. being kinda bored i decided to point a lazer straight up and do 4 flashes. from way way up there Got a HUGE super bright flash back, amazed, i kept flashing, all of a sudden got a small red and then 2 more huge bright ones back,about the size of my thumbnail if i held my hand up, same spot right off of orion's shoulder. I am wrighting this and have chills that will not go away (now about 10 min later ). I feel refreshed and rejuvinated and a lil freaked out.. man i dont even know what else to say, this was an amaizing experience. and feel very lucky.
Summary: Flashing a lazer pointer up to dark sky, got 4 flashes back
